---
title: Tomato and Mozzarella Bruschetta perfect for sharing
description: Crunchy baguette slices are topped with garlicky slow-roasted tomato, creamy mozzarella and peppery salad leaves to create a pleasing bruschetta antipasto that's simply perfetto.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_RA_R1008_W34_IE_IEA25648-2_Main_high-d14424c2.jpg
